    <h1>Types of Government</h1>
    <p>Governments are systems by which a society is organized and ruled. Different types of governments exist worldwide, varying in their structure, decision-making processes, and distribution of power. Below are some common types:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Democracy</li>
        <li>Monarchy</li>
        <li>Dictatorship</li>
        <li>Communism</li>
        <li>Federal Republic</li>
        <li>Socialism</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For a detailed explanation of these and more types of governments, visit the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Government" target="_blank">Government Wikipedia page</a>.</p>
